fullplot: His triumph over The Flea, has made Antboy hugely popular. But he is now up against a more formidable foe in the shape of the new boy in school, a smooth charmer who is fully intent on luring Ida away from Pelle. Pelle also finds himself being haunted; a brand new supervillain has announced her arrival.
plot: A superhero called Antboy fights against evil in his hometown.
title: Antboy: Revenge of the Red Fury
